{"tid":367824,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"集體回憶呀！《閃電傳真機》大聚會","createTime":"2017-08-21T05:20:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-21T13:52:17.000Z","uid":51469,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"b3a2bbbfabeacf5d97d7545647f19bb1305848d7","tid":367824,"uid":51469,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T05:20:03.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170820/bkn-20170820204332535-0820_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170820%2Fbkn-20170820204332535-0820_00862_001.html&d=nNKaX40IM0t9ZCzWUJpL%2BpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=d1eb9cb6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170820/bkn-20170820204332535-0820_00862_001.html</a><br />\n<br />\n唔知大家對兒童節目《閃電傳真機》有咩印象呢？呢個節目陪過唔少人長大㗎喇！雖然節目已經冇再做，但都成為咗唔少人嘅一個童年回憶！<br />\n<br />\n一班曾經為節目效力過嘅藝人同幕後朋友，就舉行咗一個名為「搞大咗閃電傳真機同學會」嘅派對，當然重點係大家敍吓舊，結果一呼百應，總共有六十幾人出席，當中藝人包括兒童節目始祖譚玉瑛啦，仲有黎芷珊、伍文生、麥長青、黃智賢、魯文傑、姚安娜、張沅薇、唐瑋琪、蔡子健等等，童年回憶返晒嚟！好多網民都話好感動，雖然大家未必仲一齊共事，但可以抽空聚首一堂，人情味極濃呀。<br />\n <img src=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170820/photo/bkn-20170820204332535-0820_00862_001_01p.jpg?20170820205701\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170820%2Fphoto%2Fbkn-20170820204332535-0820_00862_001_01p.jpg%3F20170820205701&h=ae560c95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\ngary哥哥同伍文生中間個男仔係邊個"},{"pid":"6b8dde10fb02b69bae3eeb412a704b001020400d","tid":367824,"uid":59602,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-21T05:54:24.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/20170820/bkn-20170820204332535-0820_00862_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fentertainment%2F20170820%2Fbkn-20170820204332535-0820_00862_001.html&d=nNKaX40IM0t9ZCzWUJpL%2BpZgE6vMW1KEzMhkvokIvkY%3D&h=d1eb9cb6\" target=\"_blank\">http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/entertainment/